{"tid":2085724,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣告！「沒有大台、只有群眾」既新時代正式開始！","createTime":"2020-06-30T04:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T12:11:38.000Z","uid":84668,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3e41bfeb9db70caaa7292aa52eb3bd07434ffcc4","tid":2085724,"uid":84668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:09:25.000Z","msg":"經過2019年，大家都明白抗爭係並非由少數英雄帶領<br />\n而係人人都可以成為英雄，無需要任何人作領袖<br />\n<br />\n大家現在見各少自決政黨解散<br />\n可能係因為害怕黨安法<br />\n但只代表舊世代既失敗抗爭方式(政治領袖大台)正式收皮<br />\n<br />\n2020年7月開始<br />\n將會正式完全進入「沒有大台只有群眾」既新時代！<br />\n<br />\n黨安惡法只係加速左新時代既來臨<br />\n用返中國戰狼既說法: <br />\n「搬起石頭砸自己的腳」<br />\n真不愧係總加速師<br />\n<br />\n一切只係剛剛開始<br />\n大家準備好迎接新時代既來臨未？<br />\n第一炮 71 sogo大減價 大家一齊振興經濟 香港再出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(頭盔 : 反對一切犯法行為)"},{"pid":"112b700baca7462184e1d82df1da3284f3e0d211","tid":2085724,"uid":335303,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:09:56.000Z","msg":"去邊？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n答案係!! 維園見(7月1)&nbsp;<br />\n因為立國安法唔去維園啫係silly 癡線 冇可能會發生&nbsp;<br />\n維園發音就係 喂完  喂完  未完<br />\n而我地華人社會 習慣將last name 擺前面<br />\n所以!!!!!!! 答案就係完未<br />\n而香港人玩完未呀 係未呀<br />\n所以!!!!!!!!!!!!!答案係!!!!!!!!!7月1維園見<br />\n輕鬆 謝謝大家"},{"pid":"22100ac15f82faf886cc62ede2eb486f0a753aa2","tid":2085724,"uid":235316,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:10:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">7一維園見</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vzHhbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vzHhbe.jpg&h=c0777e33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXtg54z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXtg54z.jpg&h=eae3d5c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qizj3Rf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQizj3Rf.jpg&h=d33e105b&s={SIZE}\" /><img sr